    height={675}
    caption="Electric and stovetop picks for better pour control, steadier extraction, and easier daily brew consistency."
  />

  <h1>Best Gooseneck Kettle for Pour Over (2026)</h1>
  <p class="lead">The best gooseneck kettle for pour over is the one that gives you repeatable flow control without making your daily routine harder. We researched current Amazon listings, compared specs and long-term owner feedback, and narrowed this guide to kettles that improve consistency whether you brew one cup or a full morning batch.</p>

  <Toc items={[
    { href: '#quick-picks', label: 'Quick Picks' },
    { href: '#comparison', label: 'Comparison Table' },
    { href: '#how-we-evaluate', label: 'How We Evaluate' },
    { href: '#product-reviews', label: 'Individual Reviews' },
    { href: '#buying-guide', label: 'Buying Guide' },
    { href: '#faq', label: 'FAQ' },
  ]} />

  <section id="quick-picks">
    <QuickPicks>
